name: RollerMiner S4

name: Rolleron 741
desc: Now we start talking! Owning one of these, you definitely don’t belong to the beginners anymore.

desc: A middle-class miner for the ambitious part-time crypto enthusiast. Noticeably more powerful than the S5+, this machine will gain you more bitcoins in reward.

name: RollerMiner S9
desc: Now you are in the premier league. This powerful machine is for the advanced crypto enthusiast. Owning one of these, you definitely qualify to play with the big dogs.

name: Dragonroller 16T
desc: It’s not enough for you to play with the big boys but you want to kick ass? Than this should be the least you can start with.

name: Dream Demolisher 3000
desc: POWER BEYOND INSANITY. Brought to you by limited anniversary GOLDEN ABYSS series.

name: Chupacabra

desc: The red beast from another dimension. Strong enough to change your mining game for ages.

desc: Orange tones of the evening sun over the working town inspired this urban themed mining machine.

name: Underwater
desc: From the depths of the sea it comes. Special water cooling system allows this miner to be deeply appreciated.

name: Hokusai
desc: The bloom, the piece, the ocean. Embrace the sensation of the calm wave inside of your mining room!

name: Retro Night
desc: This is how your dream city looks like. Feeling old yet?

name: Starground
desc: This space explorer will get you to the Moon!

name: Steamwheedle
desc: The last train home, or far away from the motherland? Who cares, GET IN this mining machine!

name: Boneyard
desc: The ancient grave of the unknown creatures has been discovered by archeologists and portrayed on this mining machine. Will you dare to own it?

name: SKAM
desc: Literally a scam.

name: Gravity
desc: The force of attraction between this mining machine and your crypto rewards is indestructible. Just like gravity! Dark Star Series Miner.

name: Paradox
desc: The Fermi Paradox tells us that aliens (do not) exist. But where else would you get this cosmic miner? Dark Star Series Miner.

name: Photon
desc: Is it a particle or wave? The answer is – mining machine! Dark Star Series Miner.

name: Anti–Phaze
desc: Harmonically balanced miner. In-built speaker is set to a pleasant frequency to make you swing while you mine. Dark Star Series Miner.

name: Serenity
desc: A wave of pleasant Ether you can feel. Serenity, comfort. Keep calm and mine it!

name: Survivor
desc: Stable and confident. Survived three explosions, one end of the world and a cat scratch.

name: Candysweet
desc: What is that taste? It is shiny, round and very sweet. Is that a candy, or a Bitcoin on your tongue?

name: Ancient
desc: You won't need Lara Croft here to make this ancient wonder work. No traps, fully domesticated demon snake on your rack.

name: The Icarus
desc: Sunbeam-proof, extra wings and no melting wax – this is the new Icarus. Brings you real revenue instead of sunburns!

name: Mycelium
desc: Still think that the blue whale is the biggest creature in the world? Actually, a mushroom is, so the mining is better.

name: DJ Roller
desc: The music of your victory and your coins rolling to your wallet! Amazing sound and beautiful design. Oh, and it is also a miner.

name: The Nemesis
desc: Best enemy to poverty and hunger, The Nemesis looks perfect in the center of your room. If you see tentakles move – please close your eyes.

name: Shifter
desc: Mimics The Nemesis sometimes, but only when you do not see. You may keep your eyes opened all the time – he never closes his.

name: The Womb
desc: The Bloodthirsty Beast of ancient depth was called to serve to its owner. Take him and watch your rewards rising!

name: Prescilla
desc: A beautiful creature of extraterrestrial civilizations just in the middle of your mining room.

name: Pepperoni 10K
desc: Make a Pepperoni buy you pepperoni. Did you know that a pizza was the first actual purchase made using 10K bitcoins?

name: Nucleus
desc: Just see how it glints and sparkles. The pure beauty!

name: Drifter
desc: Just like the Strider, who turned out to be King Aragorn, this Drifter is much more than the eye can see. All that is gold does not glitter.

name: Grum
desc: Designed to scary away everyone who is here for your coins. Warm and gentle inside, good for mining any type of crypo. We mean, crypto.

name: Shrumee
desc: Just a box of coin-greedy shrooms, which would mine for you only. Make sure to feed them with all your love (not included in the box).

name: Guts
desc: Do not let them crawl around, or they will turn everything into coins. We won't be able to bring your dog or any family members back.

name: Blaize
desc: A proven magical artefact created to make your room shine! Originally established for mining anything shiny, including coins.

name: The Krank
desc: The Womb's twin brother. Two are better than one!

name: Nuc
desc: A life-bringing nuclear technology is now available in a form of a cute little cracked crystal.

name: Singularity
desc: Your own way to the Event Horison, where all the wealth, happiness and big bucks are waiting for you to take them! Dark Star Series Miner.

name: FB-i
desc: Rollers had the strength to survive without FB logins for the whole month! Special Reward for No-Login Survivors 2021.

name: Overgrown
desc: Old, but not less powerful, this miner stood at the origins of the crypto mining era. Time-tested quality!

name: TLM-2000
desc: Temptating-Luxury-Miner-2000 is actually the best one. Get one, relax, and see your wallets grow!

name: The Blubber
desc: The filling may be confused with lava, but it is just some jelly-fish fat. Good for moisturising the miner to make it work better. Neutral smell.

name: Armageddon
desc: We had to collapse a few planets to create a perfect formula of this miner. But it is totally worth it!

name: XLZ-1
desc: XL is for 40,000, Z adds a zero, and we forgot how to write -1 in roman digits. So, 399,999 coins is the theoretical limit, will you test?

name: Lava-Tomb
desc: Eco-friendly, pure natural earth energy packed by hamsters to a nice tomb for your mining purposes.

name: The Blup
desc: Sure you want to put it next to your Lava-Box to make a perfect tandem! Also, it sounds nice. Blup.

name: The Lush
desc: Never expected a weird bush to mine coins, huh, my sweet summer child? Caution: do not water.

name: Lava-Box
desc: Just like lava-lamp, but much more fun! You ever wanted to play "The floor is lava"?

name: XLZ-01
desc: Please accept our apologies, since the hamster who knew what are the letters in the name of the miner is on vacation after building this one.

name: The Christmas Eve
desc: As powerful as The Christmas Spirit, this miner is worth waiting the whole year! Did you get on Santa’s nice list to receive it? Christmas Time Series Miner.

name: Santa’s Flyer
desc: Quick and powerful just like Santa’s reindeers, this miner will bring you power and joy! Christmas Time Series Miner.

name: Granny’s Cake
desc: It was baked to a secret Grandma’s recipe. Mix of sweetness and power that is truly impressive. Just give it a try! Christmas Time Series Miner.

name: Dasher’s Sled
desc: The fastest reindeer of the whole pack will take you to the new level of crypto mining. Christmas Time Series Miner.

name: Gingerbread
desc: What's Christmas without candies? Get into the full holiday mining spirit with a couple of gingerbreads! Christmas Time Series Miner.

name: First Class

name: Snowy Blowy
desc: Snowy and blowy, freezy and sneezy. No matter how you feel about winter, you are sure to enjoy this miner!

name: Polar Express

desc: An Ultimate Uniminer is given to you by Future-You! Future-You wants you to mine faster than he did. And you know what? It worked! Time Travel Series Miner.

desc: He mined his way from Mezozoic Era to let you know that it's your day! This cute little fellow is much more powerfull than you think, Roller. Time Travel Series Miner.

name: Petroglyph
desc: Did you know, that a pre-historic version of Crypto was dug out recently? It is not a deer, it is a pre-historic mining hamster. Time Travel Series Miner.

name: The Sacrifice
desc: No more hamster sacrifices to be made for the Mining Gods to be pleased. Simply get this sacred miner in your room and make sure it has an honorable place on your rack! Time Travel Series Miner.

name: Acropolis
desc: One of the most beautiful structures in the World. And Greek gods totally support mining! Time Travel Series Miner.

name: Ramesses II
desc: Named after the greatest Pharaoh, this miner holds the power of all Ancient Egyptian deities. Will you dare to own it? Time Travel Series Miner.

name: Richie's Castle
desc: Ever dreamed of being a King or a Queen in your own castle? Mini-servants are waiting inside to mine for you! Time Travel Series Miner.

name: Roller Industries Co.
desc: Now that is what we call Mining Industry! Make it gain maximum speed to produce the most coins for you. Air pollution, taxes and staff strikes sold separately. Time Travel Series Miner.

name: Think-Tronik
desc: Beep, beep... Calculating your personality. 1, 2, 3... Please enter the password to your brain! Beep! This Time Travel Series miner was named after Think-Tronik in our Discord community.

name: Minellite-130
desc: This could have been the point where Starlink turns to Skyline, but Elon III Musk managed to re-programm it to mining. Time Travel Series Miner.

name: Saturn-6
desc: Now flying to Saturn is more like a business trip. Centuries of studying proved that the rings of this gas giant contain a lot of Space Crypto. Grab your space shovel and join the space-crypto fewer! Time Travel Series Miner.

name: AI-miner
desc: Introducing the AI-miner! Powerfull, concentrated and very smart. He literally knows everything, and after few years of calculating he chose mining crypto as the best way to help humans prosper. Time Travel Series Miner.

name: RollerFuture
desc: Everyone knows that crypto is the future of money. But what if we told you that RLT is the future of crypto? Think about it. Time Travel Series Miner.

name: JPEG Collectooor
desc: Everybody gangsta until “Save image as…”
